{"prompt": "Generate a sleek website for a business consulting firm. The brand color should be a deep admiral blue.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Apex Consulting</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            color: #333;\n            background-color: #f8f9fa;\n        }\n        .hero {\n            background-color: #004080;\n            color: #ffffff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 100px 20px;\n            position: relative;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n        .hero h1 {\n            font-size: 48px;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 20px;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n            max-width: 800px;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n        }\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 50px auto;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        .services h2, .about h2, .contact h2 {\n            font-size: 36px;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            color: #004080;\n        }\n        .services-grid {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));\n            gap: 30px;\n            margin-top: 40px;\n        }\n        .service-item {\n            background-color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 30px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .service-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);\n        }\n        .service-item h3 {\n            color: #004080;\n            margin-bottom: 15px;\n            font-size: 24px;\n        }\n        .service-item p {\n            font-size: 16px;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        .about-content {\n            display: flex;\n            align-items: center;\n            gap: 40px;\n            text-align: left;\n        }\n        .about-content img {\n            max-width: 400px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n        }\n        .about-text {\n            flex: 1;\n        }\n        .about-text p {\n            font-size: 17px;\n            line-height: 1.8;\n        }\n        .contact form {\n            max-width: 600px;\n            margin: 40px auto;\n            padding: 30px;\n            background-color: #ffffff;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            gap: 15px;\n        }\n        .contact input, .contact textarea {\n            padding: 15px;\n            border: 1px solid #ccc;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            font-size: 16px;\n            width: 100%;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\n        }\n        .contact button {\n            background-color: #004080;\n            color: #ffffff;\n            padding: 15px 25px;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            font-size: 18px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n            align-self: center;\n            width: auto;\n        }\n        .contact button:hover {\n            background-color: #0056b3;\n        }\n        footer {\n            background-color: #004080;\n            color: #ffffff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px 20px;\n            margin-top: 50px;\n            font-size: 14px;\n        }\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            .hero h1 {\n                font-size: 36px;\n            }\n            .container {\n                width: 90%;\n            }\n            .about-content {\n                flex-direction: column;\n            }\n            .about-content img {\n                max-width: 100%;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header class=\"hero\">\n        <h1>Apex Consulting</h1>\n        <p>Driving Growth and Innovation for Your Business.</p>\n    </header>\n\n    <section class=\"container services\">\n        <h2>Our Services</h2>\n        <div class=\"services-grid\">\n            <div class=\"service-item\">\n                <h3>Strategic Planning</h3>\n                <p>Develop clear, actionable strategies to achieve your long-term business objectives.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"service-item\">\n                <h3>Market Analysis</h3>\n                <p>Gain deep insights into your market, competitors, and customer needs.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"service-item\">\n                <h3>Operational Efficiency</h3>\n                <p>Streamline your processes to maximize productivity and reduce costs.</p>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"service-item\">\n                <h3>Digital Transformation</h3>\n                <p>Leverage technology to modernize your operations and customer experience.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"container about\">\n        <h2>About Us</h2>\n        <div class=\"about-content\">\n            <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x300/004080/ffffff?text=Our+Team\" alt=\"Our Team\">\n            <div class=\"about-text\">\n                <p>Apex Consulting is a premier business consulting firm dedicated to empowering organizations to reach their full potential. Our team of experienced professionals brings a wealth of knowledge and a data-driven approach to every project. We partner with our clients to identify challenges, uncover opportunities, and implement tailored solutions that deliver measurable results.</p>\n                <p>We believe in collaborative partnerships, working closely with your team to ensure seamless integration and sustainable success.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section class=\"container contact\">\n        <h2>Get In Touch</h2>\n        <form action=\"#\" method=\"post\">\n            <input type=\"text\" name=\"name\" placeholder=\"Your Name\" required>\n            <input type=\"email\" name=\"email\" placeholder=\"Your Email\" required>\n            <textarea name=\"message\" placeholder=\"Your Message\" rows=\"6\" required></textarea>\n            <button type=\"submit\">Send Message</button>\n        </form>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Apex Consulting. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}